# Frontend Directory

This directory will contain the Next.js web application.

## Structure
```
frontend/
├── src/
│   ├── components/      # React components
│   ├── pages/           # Next.js pages
│   ├── services/        # API services
│   ├── store/           # Redux store
│   ├── utils/           # Utility functions
│   └── styles/          # Global styles
├── public/              # Static assets
├── tests/               # Test files
└── package.json         # Dependencies
```
